{
  "texts": [
    "This discussion aims to guide researchers who are seeking to advance GC further.The structure of this survey is outlined as follows: Section 2 delves into the definition, criteria, and taxonomy of GC.",
    "Following this, Section 3 discusses the optimization strategies employed in GC methods.",
    "Section 4 provides a thorough investigation of each category of GC, as aligned with our taxonomy.",
    "In Section 5, we extensively discuss the methods involved in condensed graph generation, and Section 6 empirically compares the representative GC methods across diverse evaluation criteria.",
    "Section 7 is dedicated to summarizing the various applications and resources of GC."
  ]
}